                If an account matching your email exists, then an email was just sent that contains a link you can use to reset your password.
                This link will expire in <span class="font-semibold text-gray-700">
                    {{ resetToken.expirationMessageKey|trans(resetToken.expirationMessageData, 'ResetPasswordBundle') }}
                </span>.
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-600">
